  article.cost
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12.col-sm-12.col-xs-12
           h2.headline.text-center
            | A Guide to the cost of Varicose Veins Treatments

           p
            | We treat all patients as individuals. A consultation will take place during which:
            ul.marked-list
              li your consulant will listen to your concerns and what you would like treated
              li your consulant will talk to you about your medical history and perform a full examination
              li any findings will be explained to you and the cause of your varicose veins explained
              li nearly all patients with bulging varicose veins will require a ultrasound scan
              li a treatment plan for you will be planned and the treatment options discussed with you
            
          p
            | The table below provides a guide to the cost of your treatment as your individual treatment plan
            | will be taylored to you.
            
